    public interface IClientServerToSignalMapping

        long getLengthClientId()
        Query the value of the attribute LengthClientId.

        This attribute defines the length of the used client identifier in bits. If the attribute does not exist or its value is set to 0 this means that the client identifier is not used. Please note that this attribute is deprecated and will be removed in future (Value is fixed to UInt16).
